Here's how to set up runtime theme switching in .NET MAUI:

**1. Define themes as `ResourceDictionary` files:**

```xml
<!-- Themes/LightTheme.xaml -->
<ResourceDictionary xmlns="http://schemas.microsoft.com/dotnet/2021/maui"
                    xmlns:x="http://schemas.microsoft.com/winfx/2009/xaml">
    <Color x:Key="PrimaryColor">#1A73E8</Color>
    <Color x:Key="BackgroundColor">#FFFFFF</Color>
    <Color x:Key="TextColor">#212121</Color>
    <!-- ... -->
</ResourceDictionary>
```

Create matching `DarkTheme.xaml` and `HighContrastTheme.xaml` with the same keys but different values.

**2. Create a theme service:**

```csharp
public enum AppTheme { Light, Dark, HighContrast }

public static class ThemeService
{
    public static void ApplyTheme(AppTheme theme)
    {
        var mergedDicts = Application.Current!.Resources.MergedDictionaries;
        mergedDicts.Clear();

        var themeDictionary = theme switch
        {
            AppTheme.Dark => new DarkTheme(),
            AppTheme.HighContrast => new HighContrastTheme(),
            _ => new LightTheme()
        };

        mergedDicts.Add(themeDictionary);

        // Persist the choice
        Preferences.Set("app_theme", theme.ToString());
    }

    public static void LoadSavedTheme()
    {
        var saved = Preferences.Get("app_theme", nameof(AppTheme.Light));
        if (Enum.TryParse<AppTheme>(saved, out var theme))
            ApplyTheme(theme);
    }
}
```

**3. Apply on startup in `App.xaml.cs`:**

```csharp
public App()
{
    InitializeComponent();
    ThemeService.LoadSavedTheme();
}
```

**4. Settings page (switch on selection):**

```csharp
void OnThemePicked(object sender, EventArgs e)
{
    var selected = (AppTheme)themePicker.SelectedIndex;
    ThemeService.ApplyTheme(selected);
}
```

**5. Consume in XAML with `DynamicResource`** (not `StaticResource`):

```xml
<Label TextColor="{DynamicResource TextColor}"
       Text="Hello, themed world!" />
```

`DynamicResource` is critical — it re-evaluates when the dictionary changes, giving you instant theme switching without restarting the app.
